{"title":"驼队在苍黄中跋涉","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"驼队在苍黄中跋涉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浊天的沙柱狂旋着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风也苍黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云也苍黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍黄中驼队昂首跋涉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驼铃摇荡着呼啸的荒凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大漠落日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆，圆圆地浮在地平线上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衬凸出耸峙的驼峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋进者立体的铜像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳、芨芨草、骆驼刺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风沙，埋不殁生命力的顽强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿，又钻出沙包摇曳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇曳不落的心旌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着远方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方，苍黄的地平线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风旋沙卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾似的凄迷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许百里觅不见一滴水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙市蜃景，诱惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷失方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只闻驼铃摇响一支出塞曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压倒风沙不协和的重唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚幻不可惑乱心旌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈步坚定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驼队直入大漠洪荒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，穿过苍黄的尽头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面就是山青日朗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉，纵然渴倒在沙漠里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头，永远举向有水有草有花的前方。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}